data.description: Beautiful, newly painted, 6 bed/3 bath, 4-acre horse property located in the heart of Marion. Close to the Post Office, Marion School, bakery and restaurants and just a short drive to Little Bitterroot Lake & other nearby lakes. A fisherman, hunter, and equestrian dream! This home features vaulted ceilings, woodstove to warm the entire house and walk out deck with views of the mountains. The laundry room includes stackable washer & dryer.  A full walk-out basement offers 2 bedrooms, full bath, a gym room with egress, storage room, utility room, pet room, and a small kitchenette. A hot tub pad has been prepped outside. The privacy fence with double 8' tall gate out front makes for a peaceful home. Detached 30x40 insulated 2 car garage/shop, wired for 110/220. RV pad set up behind the shop with 30 Amp electrical hookup. Horse pasture fenced & ready for your horses. Contact Troy Ewing at 406-253-7315, or your real estate professional.
